column3: Riding around Panta de Sau, my area! Love it.
You make me wanna ride and buy more rapha stuff! We need more movies, more food, more high end good stuff
Love the channel but jeeze, anyone who has done touring will look at 0.24 sec and worry about that  tail wagging the dog!
I don't like it, I LOVE IT
love this channel, whatever you think of the brand, you can't deny you just want to get out there and ride!
